{"tid":1878953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢醫院開禁藥！ 藥單有甘草片含鴉片成份","createTime":"2020-02-14T01:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T02:54:33.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"569836664ef06aacdbceee68b4f9da8158450a8d","tid":1878953,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:53:10.000Z","msg":"武漢是疫症重災區，當局運用軍力，加建火神山及雷神山醫院紓解床位不足問題，另將多個場館改建成「方艙醫院」，收治輕症病人。不過，着眼看方艙醫院的藥單，除了混合使用中西藥，還包含中成藥「複方甘草片」。國家食品藥品監督管理總局前年2月曾發通知，列出大批被禁售的複方甘草片，可見用複方甘草片變相是禁忌。有香港註冊中醫師對《蘋果》指出，「複方甘草片」含有鴉片成份，長期單獨服用，會導致病患潰瘍和上癮，香港中醫師絕對不會使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200214/XU2OWS7CAZPEQ4RK4KEHULLWIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200214%2FXU2OWS7CAZPEQ4RK4KEHULLWIY%2F&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IveL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=4799db49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200214%2FXU2OWS7CAZPEQ4RK4KEHULLWIY%2F&h=ad7208e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200214/XU2OWS7CAZPEQ4RK4KEHULLWIY/</a>"},{"pid":"3262e233ae2c3ecbdc137c9ca53c5106a1667757","tid":1878953,"uid":44978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:54:09.000Z","msg":"親，中醫能活死人生白骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a708c38631f4bcff8467ef669b0892625d3f84f0","tid":1878953,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:54:47.000Z","msg":"自稱家傳中醫、主治中醫師、北中醫（北京中醫藥大學）碩士的認證微博用戶「國醫東方」7日發帖，分享方艙醫院病人的日常用藥，可見有國家衞健委的中藥「二號方」，成份包括生黃芪10克、炒白朮10克、防風10克、貫眾10克、金銀花10克、佩蘭10克、陳皮6克，煎服，每日一付，分2次，療程7至10日。方艙醫院病人需在早晚飯後40分鐘，各服一次。<br />\n<br />\n另服複方甘草片、蓮花清瘟膠囊。西藥包括監酸莫西沙星片（抗生素）、頭孢地尼膠囊（抗生素）、左氧氟沙星片（抗流感藥）、磷酸奧司他韋膠囊（特敏福藥）。"},{"pid":"0e4686f26d4d7cae8bc3548cbb58069f7697ab7a","tid":1878953,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:55:10.000Z","msg":"值得留意的是，藥單上包括被禁售、有鴉片成份的複方甘草片。國家食品藥品監督管理總局於前年2月發通知，指大批被禁售的複方甘草片，成份主要為甘草流浸膏粉、阿片粉、樟腦、八角茴香油、苯甲酸鈉，其中，「阿片粉」即是鴉片，有報道指，持續服用逾5天，可出現快感，逐漸成癮。央視亦曾報道，列出複方甘草片的缺點，包括易成癮、過量服用會抑壓中樞神經、加重肝腎負擔。"},{"pid":"77a545fd3dc4a234b5ebe81fe4ff9a18731b7425","tid":1878953,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:55:28.000Z","msg":"香港註冊中醫師朱穎詩指出，沒聽過香港有醫師使用中成藥「複方甘草片」，因為當中的鴉片成份有毒性，有毒性的藥品要經過嚴格審批程序才可使用。不過，她指出甘草是中醫常用藥，不同用量有不同用途，用量大的話，專治心氣虛，即指心跳急促的病徵；用量小的話，多數用來調和藥性。朱醫師補充，涼性的生甘草泡水飲，可治熱性乾咳。<br />\n<br />\n另一名香港註冊中醫師陳國正則指，國內的特性是「中西醫不分家」，因此聽到方艙醫院混合使用中西藥，不感出奇，「有時中醫甚至會開西藥，同埋佢哋（內地醫生）（用藥）會大膽啲，例如甘草片。」但香港、台灣肯定是「中還中，西還西」。"},{"pid":"241976457b3d486737bb70632b8c3c3d026f7f04","tid":1878953,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"個病好返，但病人死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ead5abd242aa0687efa5614883b06624d621b29","tid":1878953,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"終蟈豬淨食鴉片都可以存活一年 !"},{"pid":"5e5690964f1d623ebcf08f47db837d3269f336c0","tid":1878953,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"東亞病夫2020"},{"pid":"ac1d8d097ab0833558502e6758d0840abafb6f70","tid":1878953,"uid":99420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77b7c5a814eb4a77ef3d068027c083e38510ad05","tid":1878953,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"大煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5780882268f073afa7c35f62b795009af7abe7d0","tid":1878953,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:58:05.000Z","msg":"中國用親鴉片之後都唔見有咩好野"},{"pid":"ce6707d3fb61dbb234cc991b981e1150817df4c6","tid":1878953,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:58:53.000Z","msg":"唔差在一邊食 一邊播首萬里長城永不倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e208c8ee6018bf3e28c4930a0167899f82d2e217","tid":1878953,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"死馬當活馬醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b5302a508bd1896477b2f3e2c9c75c79b7245e","tid":1878953,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77b7c5a814eb4a77ef3d068027c083e38510ad05","tid":1878953,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"大煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:01:41.000Z","msg":"化啖止咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e664204079bdc060d4f5f9ecf1a9f95e531eb25","tid":1878953,"uid":291465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"好fake人，甘草可以調和不同中藥之間既毒性。多幾隻字既甘草片就有鴉片成分既禁藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6700f7545d9e6c8663f99e454297aabf19f1cf77","tid":1878953,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"潮流果然係不斷循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinacn/w648h451/20171210/15d4-fypnsip5350448.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinacn%2Fw648h451%2F20171210%2F15d4-fypnsip5350448.png&h=46f0f654&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39007e377e676fbc73232b0a3ba258f4c86c135e","tid":1878953,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:11:12.000Z","msg":"Opioid induced gastric ulcer??"},{"pid":"3c6ec48cece72058ba1ef07e4447ee2494d3410b","tid":1878953,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"只要係其他原因死<br />\n就唔算係因武漢肺炎死亡"},{"pid":"063e98e43335e44e1b054e2fb02f8959ed558715","tid":1878953,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:35:39.000Z","msg":"唔怪得王偽話疫症後經濟會大力反彈啦，多左幾億人吸毒，肥肥啦"},{"pid":"5ad924e51934aa41fcdd74f715d7da02beb128d4","tid":1878953,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"死之前俾啲正嘢同志 high 下 jei"},{"pid":"8e6b2ce1dd00e03fe888aa2bfc67fdf9c118e55c","tid":1878953,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"繼續亂落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}